<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <h1>Thanks !</h1>
    <p>
      Your ad has been saved.
    </p>
    <p>
      However, to definitively confirm your ad (and your email address), please click on the link provided
      in the confirmation email that has just been sent to you, within 24 hours.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you do not answer within this time, your ad will be automatically deleted.
    </p>
    <p>
      The organizing team.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Practical shortcuts</h2>
    <p>
      To duplicate the ad you just saved, click the button below. The form will be pre-filled in 
      the same form, except for the date of the trip.
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= link_to 'Copy path', new_from_copy_trip_path(@trip), class: 'btn btn-warning' %>
    </p>
    <br/>
    <p>
      To offer the return trip of your ad, click on the button below. The form will be
      pre-filled automatically, the departure and arrival cities will be reversed (as well as your possible steps).
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= link_to 'Create the return trip', new_for_back_trip_path(@trip), class: 'btn btn-warning' %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
